A One-way Delay Metric for IPPM
1999", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This memo defines a metric for one-way delay of packets across Internet paths. [STANDARDS-TRACK]", style=filled, fillcolor=green, fontsize=18, penwidth=3, fontweight=bold]; 

